wings_of_first_flight.name: Wings of First Flight
wings_of_first_flight.desc: A stylized wind glider that bears the passionate longing of an Outrider.

wings_of_companionship.name: Wings of Companionship
wings_of_companionship.desc: A stylized wind glider upon which is inscribed the wish to soar together.

wings_of_descension.name: Wings of Descension
wings_of_descension.desc:
Effective only on the following platform:
"PlayStation Network"
A stylized wind glider that can be used to cross the celestial heights.

wings_of_azure_wind.name: Wings of Azure Wind
wings_of_azure_wind.desc: A stylized wind glider gifted to you as a mark of Mondstadt's acknowledgment and recognition.

wings_of_golden_flight.name: Wings of Golden Flight
wings_of_golden_flight.desc: A stylized wind glider gifted to you as a mark of Liyue's acknowledgment and recognition.

wings_of_concealing_snow.name: Wings of Concealing Snow
wings_of_concealing_snow.desc: A stylized wind glider left behind by a bird of prey that once soared among these mountains.

wings_of_feasting.name: Wings of Feasting
wings_of_feasting.desc: A pair of wings that memorialize great banquets or ordinary dinners. All the enjoyment of a feast for the price of a simple meal.

wings_of_the_stormstrider.name: Wings of the Stormstrider
wings_of_the_stormstrider.desc: A stylized wind glider gifted to you as a mark of Inazuma's acknowledgment and recognition.

wings_of_shimmering_galaxy.name: Wings of Shimmering Galaxy
wings_of_shimmering_galaxy.desc: A stylized wind glider and a gift that celebrates a symphony that resounds across the stars.

wings_of_the_forest.name: Wings of the Forest
wings_of_the_forest.desc: A stylized wind glider gifted to you as a mark of Sumeru's acknowledgment and recognition.
